{
  "stem": "20021.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I lived there and the talk was about this resettlement, you see.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, people with jobs like we had, in a factory which was classified as number one importance-- there were all kinds of classifications like mostly three or four-- but because this factory worked for the Germans, supplying them what they needed for the-- they were building at the front, you know, improvised housing and so forth which needed to cover was the tar paper.",
      "word_count": 66
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the tar paper was very critical.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that factory had this number one designation and anybody who worked there had papers that he worked for the number one designation so he was safe from this first resettlement.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was fairly safe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It looked at that point that probably they would never touch me-- somebody like me because I was young and I was working.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I had a premonition at that point practically nobody else had.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody at the time knew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And very few Jews at that point left to do what I did, which is on one Saturday, I took off my yellow star, which I had here-- everybody had to wear a yellow star.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When did that start?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That started in 1939, right when the Germans arrived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right from day one, everybody had to have a yellow star.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the first order of business, you see.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I just took off to yellow star and right-- went to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't have any documents at that point yet, I didn't have any papers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I went to the railroad station, bought a ticket for Lwow and went to Lwow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's a funny story.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
